name: Thurston County Public Health Medical Reserve Corp

info:
This is a Moderna vaccination event for anyone age 18 and older. 

• This is a drive-thru clinic at South Puget Sound Community College (SPSCC), use the Crosby Blvd entrance. The clinic time is from 12:00PM - 5:00PM. After you register, you can show up at any time during the clinic to be vaccinated.• Please bring a form of identification with you to your appointment - ID card, passport, or other document with your name and birthday on it.• Wear a short-sleeved shirt, but dress with layers, if necessary. • Waiting at least 15 minutes after vaccination is required.
